Emacs::PDE version 0.01
================

PDE is a collection of extension and configuration for perl
programming using Emacs.


INSTALLATION

To install PDE, add the following to your ~/.emacs:

     (add-to-list 'load-path "/path/to/pde/")
     (load "pde-load")

DEPENDENCIES

None.

